or: red;\">＊記住，公開留言先有用！＊</span></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">＊＊＊＊＊</div><strong>TVB廣告客戶名單(持續更新) ：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=ef3a909d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">＊＊＊＊＊</div><strong>跟進：</strong><br />\n1. 無論公司如何回應，如未再發現相關廣告，將暫被列入觀察名單/白名單，若發現再有廣告，將再被列入黑名單。請大家點到即止；<br />\n2. 此抵制運動必須<span style=\"color: red;\">維持最少至本年10月</span>，即是TVB與客戶商討下年廣告合約期間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/gVRvHWD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVRvHWD.jpg&h=418b291b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"大家集中攻擊第五波廣告客戶先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【抵制TVB廣告客戶 - 第五波】</strong> </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>日本獅王 - Pair抗痘洗面膏/ 休足時間</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lifelovelion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flifelovelion%2F&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=d5e246ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lifelovelion/</a> (TW FB only)<br />\nenquiry@lionhp.com.hk<br />\n替代：娥羅納英<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>大班麵包西餅 - 冰皮月餅</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/taipan.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftaipan.c